        <circle cx="311.949" cy="25.1095" r="10" data-logo-dot/>
      </svg>
    </a>
  </header>

  <div class="page">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="hero-label">Independent software from Turku, Finland</div>
      <h1 data-hero-line>Software that's<br />built to last.</h1>
    </section>
    <div class="scroll-cue" data-scroll-cue aria-hidden="true">
      <span class="scroll-cue-label">Scroll</span>
      <span class="scroll-cue-track">
        <span class="scroll-cue-segment"></span>
      </span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section-line-wrap">
    <div class="section-line section-line--right" data-section-line></div>
  </div>

  <div class="page">
    <section class="about" data-about>
      <h2 data-about-line>Finnvek</h2>
      <p data-about-line>Finnvek is independent software from Turku, Finland. I'm one developer, working on my own projects.</p>
      <p data-about-line>It exists because some ideas were worth following, and I had the freedom to follow them. The kind of ideas that stay interesting for years, not weeks. The kind I care about enough to build carefully, without shortcuts or rushed releases.</p>
      <p data-about-line>Every product is its own thing. No ads, no tracking. Made to work well, and to keep working for a long time.</p>
      <p data-about-line>The first one is <span class="accent">KnitTools</span>. More are on the way.</p>
      <div class="signature" data-about-line>&mdash; Emma</div>
    </section>
  </div>

  <div class="section-line-wrap">
    <div class="section-line section-line--left" data-section-line></div>
  </div>

  <div class="page">
    <section class="knittools" data-knittools>
      <div class="knittools-image" data-knittools-image data-parallax-wrap>
        <img src="/knittools-phone.png" alt="KnitTools app on a phone" width="862" height="1825" />
      </div>
      <div class="knittools-content">
        <div class="label" data-knittools-line>Coming soon</div>
        <h2 data-knittools-line>KnitTools</h2>
        <p data-knittools-line>KnitTools is a pocket companion for knitters. It counts your rows, reads your patterns, and keeps your stash quietly in order, with voice and AI that speaks knitter. In eleven languages, for Android.</p>
        <dl class="product-meta" data-knittools-line>
          <div>
            <dt>Status</dt>
            <dd>Coming soon</dd>
          </div>
          <div>
            <dt>Platform</dt>
            <dd>Android</dd>
          </div>
          <div>
            <dt>Languages</dt>
            <dd>11</dd>
          </div>
        </dl>
        <form class="notify-form" data-notify-form data-knittools-line>
          <label class="visually-hidden" for="notify-email">Email address</label>
          <input id="notify-email" name="email" type="email" placeholder="email address" autocomplete="email" required />
          <button type="submit">Notify me at launch</button>
        </form>
        <div class="knittools-actions" data-knittools-line>
          <a href="https://knittoolsapp.com" class="link-primary">knittoolsapp.com &rarr;</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

  <footer class="site-footer" data-reveal>
    <div class="footer-inner">
      <div class="footer-brand">Finnvek</div>
      <div class="footer-meta">
        <div class="footer-facts">
          <span>Turku, Finland</span>
          <span>2026</span>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-links">
          <a href="mailto:contact@finnvek.com">contact@finnvek.com</a>
          <a href="/privacy">Privacy</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</BaseLayout>

<script>
  import '../scripts/home-animations';
</script>
